comments.content: There are probably several fonts like this. One is certainly [FF Dynamoe](http://web.archive.org/web/20081201112002/http:/www.fontshop.com/fonts/downloads/fontfont/ff_dynamoe_exp/).

Not an exact match, but some of the members of the [Carbon 14 family](http://web.archive.org/web/20081201112002/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/coniglio/carbon14/) are close

Jason C
